text: Sahibzada Farooq Anwar Abbasi was a Pakistani politician who was member of the Provincial Assembly of the Punjab, National Assembly of Pakistan and of the royal family of Bahawalpur State. He died in 2013. ==References== Category:2013 deaths Category:Bahawalpur royal family Category:Pakistani MNAs 1990–1993
title: Sahibzada Farooq Anwar Abbasi
